author: COMSOL
description: This example demonstrates the Additional Intercalating Material feature in the Lithium-Ion Battery interface. The model describes a lithium-ion battery with two different intercalating materials in the positive electrode, whereas the negative electrode consists of one intercalating material only. The battery performance during discharge for different mix fractions of the two intercalating materials in the positive electrode is studied.
